    {
      "key": "contribution.{FreeTrain-Shika-RailroadTrain-DD51-hokuto-Cassiopeia-2}.description",
      "source": "ディーゼル機関車DD51(北斗星色)が牽引する、オール2階建寝台列車です。電源車は予備のカヤ２７です。",
      "translation": "This is an all-double-decker sleeper train pulled by a DD51 diesel locomotive (Hokutosei livery). The power car is the spare Kaya 27."
